 Laki\u0107|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=2|nat=BIH|name=[[Amar Beganovi\u0107]]|pos=DF|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=3|nat=BIH|name=Emir Jusi\u0107|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=BIH|name=Adnan Salihovi\u0107|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=SRB|name=[[Dejan Uzelac]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=8|nat=BIH|name=[[Said Husejinovi\u0107]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=9|nat=BIH|name=[[Edis Smaji\u0107]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=BIH|name=[[Samir Bekri\u0107]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=BIH|name=Amer Beki\u0107|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=12|nat=BIH|name=[[Irfan Fejzi\u0107]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=13|nat=BIH|name=Adnan Bulji\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=BIH|name=Fedor Predragovi\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=15|nat=CRO|name=Tony Livan\u010di\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=SRB|name=Du\u0161an Risti\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=BIH|name=[[Elvedin Heri\u0107]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=BIH|name=[[Almir Beki\u0107]]|pos=DF|other=[[Captain (association football)|Vice-captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=BIH|name=[[Haris Hajdarevi\u0107]]|pos=MF|other=on loan from [[FK \u017deljezni\u010dar Sarajevo|\u017deljezni\u010dar]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=SLO|name=[[Adnan Golubovi\u0107]]|pos=GK|other=on loan from [[Vis Pesaro dal 1898|Vis Pesaro]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=44|nat=SRB|name=[[Marko Marinkovi\u0107]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=55|nat=SRB|name=[[Milo\u0161 Stojanovi\u0107 (footballer, born 1997)|Milo\u0161 Stojanovi\u0107]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=70|nat=BIH|name=Sa\u0161a Maksimovi\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=93|nat=BIH|name=[[Abid Mujagi\u0107]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=99|nat=BIH|name=Semir Smajlagi\u0107|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Bakir Kari\u0107|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Amar Ni\u0161i\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Haris Kotarevi\u0107|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Players with multiple nationalities===\n* {{flagicon|BIH}} {{flagicon|SRB}} Nikola Laki\u0107\n* {{flagicon|BIH}} {{flagicon|SRB}} [[Dejan Uzelac]]\n* {{flagicon|CRO}} {{flagicon|BIH}} Tony Livan\u010di\u0107\n* {{flagicon|SLO}} {{flagicon|BIH}} [[Adnan Golubovi\u0107]]\n* {{flagicon|BIH}} {{flagicon|NED}} Haris Kotarevi\u0107\n\n===From youth team===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Anes Mehi\u0107|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Asim Muratovi\u0107|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Eldin Omerovi\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Adi Ali\u0107|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Kenin Deved\u017ei\u0107|pos=DF|other=at [[HNK Ora\u0161je|Ora\u0161je]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=BIH|name=Dino Hod\u017ei\u0107|pos=MF|other=at [[HNK Ora\u0161je|Ora\u0161je]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Managerial history==\n*{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} Ostoja Simi\u0107 (mid 1960s)\n*{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} \u0110or\u0111e Bjelogrli\u0107 (late 60s-early 70s)\n*{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} Mi\u0107o Duvan\u010di\u0107 (??-1976)\n*{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[\u0110or\u0111e Gerum]] (1976\u20131977)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Mustafa Huki\u0107]] (June 1, 1994 \u2013 August 7, 1999)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Abdulah Ibrakovi\u0107]] (September 1, 2002 \u2013 May 31, 2003)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} Sakib Malko\u010devi\u0107 (July 1, 2008 \u2013 July 24, 2009)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Nermin Had\u017eiahmetovi\u0107]] (September 5, 2009 \u2013 November 5, 2009)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Adnan Osmanhod\u017ei\u0107]] ''(interim)'' (November 9, 2009 \u2013 December 8, 2009)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} Sakib Malko\u010devi\u0107 ''(interim)'' (December 9, 2008 \u2013 December 25, 2009)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Vlatko Glava\u0161]] (January 7, 2010 \u2013 October 27, 2010)\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia and Herzegovina}} Denis Sadikovi\u0107 (October 27, 2010 \u2013 March 8, 2011)\n